# Conky-Minimalism
A Simple Conky config

**Requires:**
  * Conky with lua support | [APT] $sudo apt install conky-all
  * lm-sensors | [APT] $sudo apt install lm-sensors

## Installation
  1. Extract the zip file
  2. Create folder ~/.conky/
  3. Move Conky-Minimalism-Elementary folder to ~/.conky/
  4. Move .conkyrc to ~/ folder (home folder)
  5. Add conky to autostart

Note: If Core temps are not displayed correctly, see line 291 in clocks.lua
